<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Freedom</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">May 03, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Almighty God,
</p>

 <p>
Free us from the prisons <br></br>
that we have built <br></br>
with the bricks of <br></br>
our own expectations, <br></br>
trapped in cells <br></br>
with invisible walls <br></br>
that confine us only <br></br>
because we let them.
</p>

 <p>
Deliver us from the temptation <br></br>
to trap others by presuming <br></br>
to know your will for them, <br></br>
and forgive us for the arrogance <br></br>
of thinking that we could ever <br></br>
constrain you with limits <br></br>
on what you can do, <br></br>
who you can save, <br></br>
and who you might call.
</p>

 <p>
In the name of Christ, <br></br>
the one who gives freedom <br></br>
to all who truly seek it,
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>



